com.vdom.comms

Interface EventHandler


  • public interface EventHandler
    These functions are called FROM WITHIN NETWORK THREADS
    • handle is called from the receiving thread
    • sendErrorHandler is called from the sending thread
    • debug is called from wherever.
    ==> handle() and sendErrorHandler() are called from DIFFERENT THREADS
